## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of extrinsic motivation in sports. The research is limited by the availability of recent studies and the potential bias in self-reported data from athletes. Additionally, the dynamic nature of motivation means that individual differences can significantly affect outcomes, which may not be fully captured in the existing literature.

